<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.    C                      Am
 Jibitip toń jerdi, qýantyp bar eldi,
.        G
 Dalama naýryz keldi.
.   Dm
 Balalar kóńildi, án-jyry órildi,
.      G         C
 Naýryz áni tógildi.

[V2]
 Ókpeli jandardy, barlyq balalardy,
 Tatýlyqqa shaqyrady.
 Isa kókten keldi, tynyshtyǵyn berdi,
 Tyńdasyn jer atyraby.

[C1]
.   C       Dm      G          C
   Ata-analar, úlkender, balalar,
.     F      G           C
   Qutty bolsyn naýryzdaryń.
.     C      Dm       G         C
   Kókke jol ashyp, Másihpen jarasyp,
.     F       G       C
   Iske assyn armandaryń.

[V3]
 Jańarsyn bári de, jasy, kárisi de,
 Naýryzda jańarý kerek.
 Júregińdi bergin, Isaǵa sen kelgin,
 Tek Ol jańa ómir beredi.</lyrics>
<title>Jibitip toń jerdi, qýantyp bar eldi РӘЖ241</title>
<hymn_number>241</hymn_number>
</song>